---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Nav from "../components/Nav.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service — holomime">
  <Nav />
  <main class="pt-28 pb-20 px-6 bg-[var(--color-warm-cream)] min-h-screen">
    <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl prose-warm">
      <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="meta">Last updated: February 24, 2026</p>

      <p>These Terms of Service ("Terms") govern your access to and use of holomime's website, software, APIs, and related services (collectively, the "Service") operated by holomime ("we", "us", or "our"). By using the Service, you agree to these Terms.</p>

      <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p>By accessing or using the Service, you confirm that you are at least 18 years old (or the age of majority in your jurisdiction) and agree to be bound by these Terms and our <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>. If you are using the Service on behalf of an organization, you represent that you have authority to bind that organization to these Terms.</p>

      <h2>2. Description of Service</h2>
      <p>holomime provides a personality engine and behavioral therapy pipeline for AI agents. The Service includes personality assessment tools, behavioral diagnosis, therapy session orchestration, training data export, and evaluation capabilities. The Service may be offered through a command-line interface, web application, API, or software library.</p>

      <h2>3. Accounts</h2>
      <p>You may need to create an account to access certain features. You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials and for all activities that occur under your account. You agree to notify us immediately of any unauthorized use.</p>

