        <li>Interfere with or disrupt the integrity or performance of the Service</li>
        <li>Circumvent any access controls or usage limits</li>
        <li>Resell or redistribute the Service without our prior written consent</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>5. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>The Service, including its software, documentation, designs, and content, is owned by holomime and protected by intellectual property laws. We grant you a limited, non-exclusive, non-transferable license to use the Service in accordance with these Terms.</p>
      <p>Open-source components of holomime are licensed under their respective licenses (e.g., MIT) as specified in the applicable repositories. These Terms do not restrict rights granted under such open-source licenses.</p>

      <h2>6. Your Data</h2>
      <p>You retain ownership of any data you provide to the Service, including personality specifications, therapy session data, and training data exports ("Your Data"). You grant us a limited license to process Your Data solely as necessary to provide the Service. We will not use Your Data to train our own models or share it with third parties except as described in our Privacy Policy.</p>

      <h2>7. Subscriptions and Payments</h2>
      <p>Certain features require a paid subscription. Subscription fees are billed in advance on a recurring basis. You may cancel at any time; cancellation takes effect at the end of the current billing period. We reserve the right to change pricing with 30 days' notice. All fees are non-refundable except as required by law.</p>

